additionalContent.text:
This year on the programme of the 4D theatre:

Follow a crazy adventure of a clumsy sheriff and his trusty horse in pursuit of a fearsome bandit in the Wild West!

An unforgettable multidimensional experience!

Open your eyes wide and hang on!

additionalContent.title: The guitar legend
additionalContent.text:
Haaz, the guitar legend

Haaz is the biggest guitar legend ever and is a member of the W.A.B band. Besides playing the guitar, he is also crazy about everything what is car-minded.

Cool all-terrain vehicles

Haaz has his own garage in which he presents his cool all-terrain vehicles. You can try out his treasures and make a test ride in pure nature, what an honour!
Jump onto the train and start on the way to adventure! Who can tell what you might discover in the unexplored places in Walibi Belgium...

additionalContent.title: Flying Balloons
additionalContent.text:
Flying Balloons

Do you love to fly? Then try your luck in a colourful balloon and fly in the blue sky.

Fibi, the water spirit

Fibi the water spirit accompanies you during the exciting flying trip. She is also the one and only W.A.B singer and of course she can sing like nobody else can. You will dream away when you hear her beautiful voice!
How many of you dare taking a seat in one of the most spectacular and thrilling attractions at Walibi? We are betting that you’ll scream your lungs out.

additionalContent.title: Get ready for…
additionalContent.text:
Get ready for…

The tram of the Calamity Mine takes you 22 meters up in a mine tunnel. Get ready for the incredible adventure through the rest of the gold mine!

The gold mine

The creaking carts lead you through a magical atmosphere: you will go across shaky bridges,  rush under a waterfall, fly over a muddy river… Only for the bravest daredevils!

Gold fever?

Did you caught the gold fever virus? Don’t worry, experience this amazing ride countless times and imagine you’re a real gold digger!

additionalContent.title: Egyptian atmosphere
additionalContent.text:
Egyptian atmosphere

Do you have any idea about how the Egyptian atmosphere feels like? In this Egyptian tomb you will discover everything about it. Watch out, because you and your team are not the only visitors.

Danger around the corner

The most terrifying monsters and mummies are hiding at the most unexpected places. And they only appear when you and your team are on your way.

Armed or not?

Luckily you are equipped with laser guns to protect yourself in this unique dark ride. The one with the best shooting skills and the highest number of points, is the winner within the team. Keep you laser gun ready and shoot!

additionalContent.title: What is about to happen?
additionalContent.text:
What is about to happen?

With its slow start, the Cobra keeps the tension up for some seconds. He keeps his victims in suspense as long as possible.

Attack!

The most unlikely moment, the snake strikes! He shoots forward and whirls you up to three times upside down.

Surprise...

As if it’s not enough, you go through this sssssssuper exciting adventure again in backward mode.

additionalContent.title: Steeply climbing
additionalContent.text:
Steeply climbing

Enjoying the fresh air during an unsuspecting dead straight climb of 77 m, steep it is… Everything around you gets smaller and smaller.

Magnificent view

On the highest peak you will enjoy a few seconds the magnificent view over the whole park. At least, if you dare to look down.

Free fall

Enjoyment, or rather the shivers, quickly turns into the thrill of your life! Get ready for a free fall at 110 km/h!

additionalContent.title: Relaxation time
additionalContent.text:
Relaxation time

Do you need to take a relaxation break with the whole family? In that case the big Merry-go-round is really suitable for you.

Bursting horses

Pick out one of the beautiful horses who are bursting to make a lap with you. Or take a seat in an elegant carriage for all of you. Relaxation and nostalgia guaranteed!

additionalContent.title: Can you handle the crazy waves?
additionalContent.text:
Can you handle the crazy waves?

Hoist the sails, take your paddles and sail across the wild sea. Conquer the crazy waves.

Vikings

Imagine you’re a brave Viking and take up the challenge against the other Dragon’s boats at sea.

additionalContent.title: What exactly is the Flash Back?
additionalContent.text:
What exactly is the Flash Back?

The Flash Back is another name for a long ride in a calmly lapping boat, combined with here and there some tricky bends and short but strong descents.

Surprising turn

Suddenly the boat makes a U-turn and goes further backwards. At the right moment it turns back again because…

Finishing touch

As finishing touch you will come face to face with the steepest descent ever seen, slide down and get an inevitable shower free and for nothing.

additionalContent.title: Dreams come true
additionalContent.text:
Dreams come true

Are you dreaming of a ride on a magic carpet? Walibi fulfils your dreams.

Desert flight

Experience this magical flight through the desert with the whole family. A laughable sensation of which you cannot get enough.
Become a real pilot! Take off and discover this new children’s roller coaster.

additionalContent.title: Feeling for rhythm
additionalContent.text:
Feeling for rhythm

Move up and down on the rhythm of the music composed by Walibi himself, leader of the W.A.B band.

Mini rocket

Float from your mini rocket through the sky surrounded by the clouds at a mild speed.
Full speed ahead and kick it ! That is what the Go Karting is made for. Experience fun on this crazy circuit.

The calm and serenity of a boat ride while gazing at natural décor. Here’s one attraction that will allow you to take the time to let your hair down and breathe the fresh air. Come back to nature and get to know some aquatic birds.

additionalContent.title: Zenko and graffiti!
additionalContent.text:
Zenko and graffiti!

Zenko, top drummer of the W.A.B band, has sprayed yellow and blue graffiti on his shuttle, probably his favourite colours.

Zenko as pilot?

Hold very tight ‘cause Zenko drives his flashy shuttle all by himself. So fasten your seat belt for this

additionalContent.title: The Dalton Terror’s little brother
additionalContent.text:
The Dalton Terror’s little brother

The Guitar Riff is the little brother of the Dalton Terror, and the smallest daredevils are wild about it!

Free fall

The lift for six persons firstly goes up very slowly till it reaches the top of the Guitar. A few standstill moments,  are followed by a breathtaking free fall. Do you dare to step into this brave attraction?
Two spirits, Zanzar and Babas, deploy all of their magic powers. After a visit to this fantastic house, you won’t be able to distinguish the floor from the ceiling.

additionalContent.title: Pilot
additionalContent.text:
Pilot

What would you like to become in the future? A pilot? Then this attraction is meant just for you.

First flying experience

Go aboard, take your controls and take off, and choose how high you want to fly yourself! Your first flying experience is finished, now you are ready to become the best pilot ever.

additionalContent.title: Freedom
additionalContent.text:
Freedom

From the hanging seats, children can discover what freedom means. They can have a short break and enjoy a light breeze.

For the youngest sprigs

Little Swing is decorated with prohibition signs… That can only be a joke of the SkunX. So, only for the youngest sprigs!

additionalContent.title: Wooden design
additionalContent.text:
Wooden design

Werewolf is a roller coaster that is entirely made of wood. This produces a suitable creaky effect during the ride full of variation.

80 km/h

The red and green carts go screaming round the sharp bends at a continuous speed of 80 km/h. Hair in the wind, screams of excitement, and silly faces on the photo!

Hilly track

We break the ice with a descent which gives you the kick of your life, followed by another ten dizzy hills.

One of the oldest and most famous attractions of Walibi Belgium ! At the wheel of one of these old rattletraps, the whole family can take a ride at limited speed in the midst of dense but pleasant vegetation and spend a magic moment.

additionalContent.title: W.A.B
additionalContent.text:
W.A.B

Make a ride with this train and meet your biggest fans of the W.A.B band : Fibi, Walibi, Zenko and Haaz, they are all present!

The SkunX Mini Tour?

Look out because the SkunX are not for away. Squad would be too happy to transform the train into “The SkunX Mini Tour”.

additionalContent.title: Go to battle against the Octopus
additionalContent.text:
Go to battle against the Octopus

The Octopus takes you into its tentacles, swings you back and forth, up and down, and spins round countless runs. Do you dare to take up the challenge?

Disorientation

Whether you resist or not, you’ll be put in a flurry anyway. To find back your orientation, you would do better to have a ten-minute break!

additionalContent.title: Cowboy is coming
additionalContent.text:
Cowboy is coming

Do you like to play ‘Cowboy and Indian’ at home? Here you game comes to life! Now you are a real cowboy. Experience a true adventure!

Pony ride

To fully complete the adventure, you can pick out an untamed pony. Make an intense ride through the Indian’s town. Watch out for bow and arrow!

Ready for the adventure?

Go on an immersive journey into the world of cinema. Discover this new attraction with your family and beat the popcorn.

additionalContent.title: The myth is back again!
additionalContent.text:
The myth is back again!

Do you remember the Sirocco? Or rather the Turbine? Then now (re)discover the Psyké Underground, a legendary attraction!

In absolute darkness…

Unlike his predecessors, the Psyké Underground is covered from top to toe. This boosts the adrenaline twice as hard! Nowhere else in the world you can go through this unique experience in absolute darkness.

Catapult

The Psyké catapults you in less than 3 seconds to more than 85 km/h in a mega loop at a height of 45 meters. Don’t miss this thrilling ride!

additionalContent.title: Worlds first
additionalContent.text:
Worlds first

PULSAR will give you sensations that you want to share with friends and family.

100 kmh

Get ready for an amazing ride. Three powerfull propultions will get you up to 100 kmh.

Huge splash

Not afraid of some water? Get ready for the huge splash!

45m high

Enjoy a freefall dive into the water from 45m high.

additionalContent.title: Rapids river
additionalContent.text:
Rapids river

The Radja River, a rapids, full of sharp bends, surprising waterfalls and … tricky whirlpools. If you love adventure, you can’t miss this attraction for the world.

With 12 others in a boat

Don’t worry, you don’t have to go through this heroic adventure all by yourself. You get a round inflatable boat with 12 seats. This will be nothing but sensation and excitement.

Rafting

Rafting on the Radja River for minutes and minutes with family and friends. Hold tight cause here we go! A wet adventure guaranteed!
Turn and turn and turn again to exotic rhythm… that’s what the Salsa Y Fiesta is all about! But don’t go there just after a meal!

additionalContent.title: Taxi driver?
additionalContent.text:
Taxi driver?

Would you like to be taken by a taxi driver or do you prefer to drive yourself? It’s up to you. But watch out because there could be a traffic policeman in the neighbourhood.

Click your belt!

Click your belt because these race cars lead you to a busy road where you sometimes will have to make unexpected bends. So be careful!
Spinning Vibe is an ride that is fun for the whole family, a merry-go-round with hazardous rotations.

Squad, the famous SkunX singer

Squad, the famous singer of the SkunX, drags you into a fantastic stunt plane! Fasten your seat belt, ‘cause off we go!

Flying path

The stunt plane obviously doesn’t fly in a straight line, but follows his own path. He takes off, he gives you the feeling as if he will land, but just to the surface he shoots straight as an arrow in the sky again. It keeps going like this for a few times!

additionalContent.title: Mini train
additionalContent.text:
Mini train

The smallest sprigs will totally feel at ease in the Tchou-tchou Express. The rails lie through the heart of the band’s musical world.

A peaceful tour

The train makes a peaceful tour through a little village surrounded by cosy little houses. Intended for the youngest free-livers.
Would you like a nice overview of Exotic World ? Or do you want to climb and scramble over and around funcoaster Tiki-Waka ? Be sure to test out Tiki-Trail !

additionalContent.title: Exotic fun
additionalContent.text:
Exotic fun

Tiki-Waka invites families to enjoy a crazy ride on an exotic circuit ! Discover this new family funcoaster that can reach up to 55km / h in Walibi.

additionalContent.title: 100 % play fun
additionalContent.text:
100 % play fun

In this huge tree house each playful child can live it up for 100 %. The children are being accompanied by W.A.B, but also Squad is never far away to play a dirty trick on someone.

Refreshment

On hot summer days, the big water playground evidently will be started off. That way the little scouts can take some refreshment.

Message to mum and dad

Mum and dad, don’t worry, your little kids can play like crazy and till they’re totally tired in all security.

additionalContent.title: Traffic rules?
additionalContent.text:
Traffic rules?

In the Tuf Tuf Club traffic rules do not exist. The cars are made for bumping, so make the most of that privilege.

Have a great bumping time!

Pick out an innocent victim to crash at or venture to ride into a multiple crash. Bumping fun guaranteed!

additionalContent.title: Feet in the air
additionalContent.text:
Feet in the air

Did you ever hang in the air? In this attraction you get that feeling. Let your feet have a breath of fresh air in this true vampire ride.

Bloody stunts

A couple of bloodthirsty loops and a trio of rotations on your axis at an unseen speed… squeeze all the blood out of your body.

Extremely useful advice

You would do better to take off your shoes with loose shoelaces. Or tie them strongly up.

additionalContent.title: A swing merry-go-round
additionalContent.text:
A swing merry-go-round

A combination of a swing and a merry-go-round, that’s how you can best describe the Wave Swinger.

Tickles in your stomach

Are you well fastened because this dizzy merry-go-round sways you around and goes up and down. The tickles in your stomach won’t be missing!
A quick bite before you will defy cowboys ? The Cook House Club has a wide selection of snacks, sandwiches, beverages and smoothies.
Real cowboy’s stops at the Country Cantina to eat one’s fill with tasteful spareribs, steaks and typically Belgian dishes.
Looking for something sweet? Get one of our delicious pancakes, donuts or muffins. The patio offers a beautiful view on PULSAR.
Want to eat a tasty burger, nuggets or salads in the heart of a cowboy village? The place-to-be is the Dalton Burger.

Immerse yourself in the world of Karma World and enjoy delicious Indian dishes: Tikka-Masala Chicken, Bombay Chicken and many more. Also enjoy the sublime terrace of the restaurant overlooking the lake.
Fun O'Clock Is the most irresistible patio at Walibi. In the middle of Fun World, where your cherubs will find their own paradise with all kinds of attractions just their size !
Feel like enjoying an ice cream? Visit the Ice Cream Song. To be consumed without moderation!
Enjoy an extensive breakfast with a coffee upon arrival in the park. At Java’s Coffee Corner you will find coffee but also pastries and gorgeous waffles.
La Terrasse and his pleasant patio is the place-to-be to take some rest. We serve the best Belgian beers with a portion of fries, a mitraillette or a hot-dog.
How does eating in the heart of an Italian public square sound? Come and discover the Italian restaurant. Pasta and pizzas are waiting for you.
An ice-cream or a panini, it’s always delicious! Come over at the Rock & Freeze, it’s next to the 4D Cinema.
Need something to recover from Psyké Underground ? You can have a kebab, hamburger, pastabox or an ice-cream on the wide patio of Rock Sandwich.
Need some refreshment? At Slush Ice Factory we serve you ice-cold slushs.
In front of the Dalton Terror is a concept of bar/grill in open air, the Star Saloon. Cowboys come over for a fresh drink and eat a barbecue.
A tasteful waffle or ice-cream to satisfy your hunger ? At Sweet Star you’ll be served rapidly.
Hungry ? Swing Fries has various dishes: panini’s, hamburgers, mitraillette, ice creams and it is the place-to-be for delicious fries !
Feeling thirsty in the exotic environment of Exotic World ? The cocktails and smoothies from the Tiki-Bar will refresh you. Also hungry ? Try out our delicious muffins and nachos.
Eating a hamburger with fries or a snack with a coaster right above your head ? At the Western Fries you will eat underneath the racing cars of Tiki-Waka !
If you don’t want to be bothered by your bags and packages during the day, you will find lockers available at check-in.
The candy shop offers a lot of different kinds of candys as well as traditionnal souvenirs.
The shop at the 4D cinema proposes different Walibi souvenirs and also a variety of candy and soft drinks, just what you need to extend the Walibi film experience.
Feeling your sweet tooth? At the Megamix you’ll find a large variety of candy and soft drinks starting with chocolates, then cotton candy, and chips.
Looking for a unique gift ? In the W.A.B Shop you’ll find different souvenirs of each: mugs, glasses, T shirts, cushions…
At the Western Shop you will find various western articles: cowboy hats, guns … A selection of Walibi articles is also on sale.
